            <div class="d-flex gap-2 w-100 justify-content-between">
                <div>
                    <h6 class="mb-0">Peculiaridade Oracle - 04</h6>
                    <p class="mb-0 opacity-75">Uma forma simples de mapear uma coluna do banco com uma propriedade do C# é criando um Alias no <code>SELECT</code></p>
                    <p>
                        Exemplo:
                        <strong class="text-info">C#: </strong><code>[Column("LAST_NAME")] public string LastName { get; init; } = string.Empty!;</code>
                        <br/>
                        &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&ensp;<strong class="text-info">SQL: </strong><code>SELECT ID, NAME, LAST_NAME <strong>AS LastName</strong>, EMAIL, ACTIVE FROM CLIENTS</code>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
